非递归：

```python
class Solution:
    def inorderTraversal(self, root: Optional[TreeNode]) -> List[int]:
        res = []
        if not root:
            return res
        node = root
        stack = []
        while node or stack:
            if node:
                stack.append(node)
                node = node.left
            else:
                node = stack.pop()
                res.append(node.val)
                node = node.right
        return res
```

