# 415. 字符串相加

从一个数的后面加到前面。

```python
class Solution:
    def addStrings(self, num1: str, num2: str) -> str:
        carry = False
        res = ''
        len_1 = len(num1)
        len_2 = len(num2)
        for i in range(-1, -max(len_1,len_2)-1, -1):
            if i<-len_1:
                temp = int(num2[i])
            elif i<-len_2:
                temp = int(num1[i])
            else:
                temp = int(num1[i])+int(num2[i])
            if carry:
                temp += 1
